`internal/worktree TestNoTempDirLeakOnWorktreeAddFailure` failed once in a
parallel run because the test snapshots `etude-worktree-*` temp dirs in the
shared $TMPDIR and caught a dir from another concurrent test. Passes
deterministically when run alone or in a clean second pass. Pre-existing
and unrelated to this bead.

